Single bar unit
----------------------
|           |           |
|           |           |
|           |           |
----------------------
Basic window unit with one bar.

#Maths
barSize = height - 27; // 12mm for frame, 1.5mm for a key that goes into the bar 12 +1.5 = 13.5, there is to sides so *2 = 27

Simple crossed bar unit
