This is more complicated, but not the most complicated.
bar is 18mm thick (usualy, there are different types, but we will start on this one)

#Maths
horizontalBar = width - 27 - 18; (18mm is a barThickness, I put it separatelly to make a point of reference)
verticalBar = height - 27 - 18;
